你能够调用以下的API:
[['RealEstateMarket.get_hot_markets', {'name': 'RealEstateMarket.get_hot_markets', 'description': 'This function retrieves the current hot real estate markets.', 'required_parameters': [], 'optional_parameters': [], 'return_data': [{'name': 'markets', 'description': 'A list of hot real estate markets, each containing name and location.'}]}], ['RealEstateInvestment.recommend_project', {'name': 'RealEstateInvestment.recommend_project', 'description': 'This function recommends a real estate investment project based on the user's budget and risk preference.', 'required_parameters': [{'name': 'budget', 'type': 'NUMBER', 'description': 'The investment budget.'}, {'name': 'risk_preference', 'type': 'STRING', 'description': 'The user's risk preference (e.g., low, moderate, high).'}], 'optional_parameters': [], 'return_data': [{'name': 'project', 'description': 'The recommended real estate project, containing id, name, and location.'}]}], ['RealEstateInvestment.calculate_returns', {'name': 'RealEstateInvestment.calculate_returns', 'description': 'This function calculates the potential returns of a recommended real estate investment project.', 'required_parameters': [{'name': 'project_id', 'type': 'NUMBER', 'description': 'The ID of the recommended project.'}], 'optional_parameters': [], 'return_data': [{'name': 'returns', 'description': 'The potential returns of the project, including annual yield and total return.'}]}], ['RealEstateInvestment.calculate_risks', {'name': 'RealEstateInvestment.calculate_risks', 'description': 'This function calculates the potential risks of a recommended real estate investment project.', 'required_parameters': [{'name': 'project_id', 'type': 'NUMBER', 'description': 'The ID of the recommended project.'}], 'optional_parameters': [], 'return_data': [{'name': 'risks', 'description': 'The potential risks of the project, including market risk and liquidity risk.'}]}], ['RealEstateInvestment.get_consultation_link', {'name': 'RealEstateInvestment.get_consultation_link', 'description': 'This function provides a link to a real estate investment consultation service.', 'required_parameters': [], 'optional_parameters': [], 'return_data': [{'name': 'link', 'description': 'The link to the consultation service.'}]}]]
请生成一个解决用户问题的计划，计划应该是一个行为列表，每个行为的格式如下:

[{
    // 动作的ID
    "id": number;
    // 动作要调用的API名称
    "name": string;
    // 当前API的参数输入(JSON格式)
    "args": "str(Record<string, any>)";
}, ...
]

你可以在计划中想象参数的值，这些指令将按顺序执行。
例如，如果你想调用 `api1` 并传入 `arg1` 和 `arg2`，你可以写下面的计划:

[{
    "id": 0,
    "name": "api1",
    "args": "{'arg1': 'value1', 'arg2': 'value2', ...}",
}, ...
]

这些参数将在执行时被替换为真实的值。请注意，参数应该是一个字符串，而不是一个字典。
请在字典的参数中使用 ''，在其他地方使用 ""，不要打印值为 None 或 null 的参数。

你应该只生成一个 JSON 格式的计划列表。列表应该是完整的计划列表，不要有 `...`。
不要生成任何解释 JSON 的文本。
